  "body": "### Description of the Feature\r\n\r\nWe want the nonce to update so that transactions don't fail on back-to-back transactions. Should \r\n\r\n### Steps to Reproduce\r\n\r\n1) Access your account.\r\n2) Send a transaction.\r\n3) Immediately try to send another transaction. It will fail because nonce exists, requiring users to manually-update nonce.\r\n\r\n### To Fix\r\n\r\nAllow for nonce to automatically be updated after transaction broadcast success",
